item.title: SoftLayer_Software_Component_AntivirusSpyware_Mcafee
item.description: SoftLayer_Software_Component_AntivirusSpyware_Mcafee Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Software_Component_AntivirusSpyware_Mcafee represents a single anti-virus/spyware software component. Local hardwareId Hardware Identification Number for the server this Software Component is installed upon. Type: integer id An ID number identifying this Software Component (Software Installation) Type: integer manufacturerActivationCode The manufacturer code that is needed to activate a license. Type: string manufacturerLicenseInstance A license key for this specific installation of software, if it is needed.
